com.esri.mo2.file.shp
Interface Shape

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable
All Known Subinterfaces:
ShapeM, ShapeZ
All Known Implementing Classes:
MultiPointMShp, MultiPointShp, MultiPointZShp, PointMShp, PointShp, PointZShp
public interface Shape
extends Cloneable

This class declares the methods that are common to all non-multipart shapes. The starting index for points is 0.
